title: Lisa Brennan-Jobs on 'Small Fry'
description: In a special episode of the Book Review's podcast, taped in front of a live audience, Brennan-Jobs talks about her memoir, and Gary Shteyngart discusses "Lake Success."
author: books@nytimes.com (The New York Times)
